    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>Dum in Dei nomine <rs key="#Cities">civitate</rs>
                        <placeName key="#City_territory #Assembly #Cities #Count #Bishops"
                            ref="#places/59">Verona</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Assembly">in iuditio resedissemus</rs> nos <persName
                            key="#Missus_regis #Bishops">Rataldus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopus</rs>
                        <rs key="#Missus_regis">misso domni imperatoris</rs> ad singulorum hominum
                        deliberandas intentiones, resedentes nobiscum <persName key="#Count"
                            >Hucpaldus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Count">comis</rs> ipsius civitatis, <persName key="#Judge"><name
                                ref="Andreas">Andreas</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudex</rs> et <persName key="#Notary"><name
                                ref="Bonifredus">Bonifrit</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> regalis, <persName key="#Scabini"><name
                                ref="Draco">Draco</name></persName> et <persName
                            key="#Advocatus_of_other_public_authorities #Scabini"><name
                                ref="Ragibertus">Raginpert</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Scabini">scavini</rs> ipsius civitatis, vel reliquis. Sed ipse
                        Bonifrit notarius, iusta ut nos illi commendavimus, cepit querere prefati
                        Hucpaldi comiti de parte <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Monasteries" ref="#places/15"><orgName key="#Monasteries"
                                ref="#juridical_persons/47">Nonantule</orgName></placeName> ex <rs
                            key="#Forests">silva</rs> que nominatur <placeName
                            key="#Forests #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_individuals"
                            ref="#places/2492"><geogName
                                key="#Forests #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_individuals"
                                ref="#estates/1138">Ostilia</geogName></placeName>, que posita esse
                        videtur in <rs key="#City_territory">finibus</rs> ipsius civitatis
                        Veronensi, portionem illamque fuit quondam <persName key="#Abbots"
                            ref="#people/49">Anselmi</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbati</rs> et <persName ref="#people/1260"
                            >Tadini</persName> germani eius, quorum res a prefato monasterio
                        devenerunt hoc est quartam portionem de super totum ex prefata silva et
                        medietatem de aliis tribus portionibus, quam a <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_individuals"
                            >parte regia adquisiverunt</rs>, excepto <rs key="#Landed_possessions"
                            >sorte</rs> una que pertinet ad <rs key="#Domuscultae">domumcultile</rs>
                        <rs key="#Churches">capelle</rs> regalis, quod vocabulum est <orgName
                            key="#Domuscultae #Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/1109">Sancto
                            Laurentio</orgName>, et alia sorticella que videtur esse de <rs
                            key="#Curtes">curte</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Curtes" ref="#places/572"><geogName ref="#estates/519"
                                key="#Curtes">Roverxelle</geogName></placeName>
                        <persName key="#Count" ref="#people/166">Anselmi</persName> comitis. Et
                        dicebat quod contra legem ipse Hucpaldus eam haberet. Hec nos audientes
                        commendavimus ipsius Hucpaldi, ut inquireret de causa hec si eam legibus
                        haberet, veniret ad plaido et qualis melius poterit eam defenderet. Et cum
                        nos illi hoc commendaremus, de domni imperatoris iussu, sic ipse Hucpaldus
                        commendavit suprascripto Ragimperto scavino et <rs
                            key="#Advocatus_of_other_public_authorities">avocatore</rs> suo, ut
                        exinde inquireret et a plaido plenam rationem exinde donaret. Posito plaido,
                        venientes nos instituto die in curte regia que dititur <placeName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Mention #Function #Residential"
                            ref="#places/917"><geogName ref="#estates/520"
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Mention #Function #Residential"
                                >Potiolo</geogName></placeName>, ripa <rs key="#Rivers">fluvio
                            Mentio</rs>, et cum resedissemus in ibi ad causas audiendas, resedentes
                        nobiscum <persName key="#Bishops" ref="#people/1277">Andreas</persName>
                        episcopus <placeName ref="#places/69" key="#Bishops"
                            ><orgName key="#Bishops" ref="#juridical_persons/2428">Vicentinus</orgName></placeName> et ipse Hucpaldus comis, seu
                            <persName key="#Count" ref="#people/1257">Odo</persName> comis de
                            <placeName key="#Count" ref="#places/275">Mantua</placeName> et
                        suprascripti Andreas iudex et Bonifrit, <persName><name ref="Lupus"
                                >Lupus</name></persName>, <persName><name ref="Bodonicus"
                                >Bodonicus</name></persName> et ipse Draco et Ragimpert scavinus vel
                        reliqui, sic ipse Bonifrit rettulit nobis de hac causa et dixit: “Ecce modo
                        plaido est. Volumus scire quid iste Hucpaldus comis de ipsa silva que
                        nominatur Ostilia, que pertinet ad monasterio Nonantule, ostendere vult, aut
                        pro qua causa eam contraditit”. Qui et ipse Hucpaldus comis et suprascripto
                        Raginpert advocatore eius dixerunt quod nullam rationem nec iustitiam
                        invenire potuissent, nec poterint, quomodo quartam partem et medietatem ex
                        tribus portionibus de prefata silva Ostilia, exceptis duabus sortibus, quas
                        superius nominavimus, a parte suprascripti monasterii cum lege poterint
                        contradicere. Sic de presenti ipse Hucpaldus comes per manitia sua de manu
                        eundem Bonifrit a parte prefati monasterii revestivit. Unde et pro
                        securitate eidem monasterio Nonantule hanc notitiam facere commonuimus. Ego
                            <persName key="#Notary #Writer"><name ref="Deusdedit"
                            >Deusdedit</name></persName> notarius regalis <rs key="#Writer"
                            >scripsi</rs>. Anno domni Ludoviti <rs key="#Emperor/king"
                            >imperatoris</rs> septimo, pridie kalendas aprelis, inditione
                        tertiadetima. Feliciter. Ego Rataldus episcopus missus domni imperatoris
                        manus mea subscripsi. Ego Andreas episcopus Vicentinus concordans
                        subscripsi. Andreas iudex subscripsi. Draco <rs key="#Witness"
                            >subscripsi</rs>. Ragimper scavinus subscripsi. Ego Hucpaldus comes
                        subscripsi. Ego Bonifrit notarius subscripsi. <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Gaideris">Gaderius</name></persName> subscripsi. Ego Odo comes
                        de Mantua subscripsi. Lupus subscripsi. Bodonicus subscripsi. <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Landolinus">Landolinus</name></persName>
                        subscripsi. </ab>
                </div>
